# Projects
* Ulysses *
A web app for people to make [Ulysses Contracts](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ulysses_pact) with others. Built on Django and MongoDB.

* Foodpoints+ [Github](https://github.com/chronologos) *
A web app for Duke Students to track their food spending. Built with Node.js, MongoDB, Angular.js. Has reached 250 monthly active users.

* Memento [Github](https://github.com/chronologos) *
Use Bluetooth Beacons to allow people to securely store photos at locations. Built on Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB. 1 of 10 Final Round Projects for Hackathon@SG.
